Normally this is where you'd have the git submodule
https://github.com/CarloWood/cmake-aicxx added, but
since libcwd already has that module we're simply
using a symbolic link to there.

See https://github.com/CarloWood/cmake-aicxx#adding-the-cmake-aicxx-submodule-to-a-project
for the normal install instructions.
